Content: I've been looking for a MM recipe to use rhubarb, a fav in this area now, so I'm thinking I may use 1/2 rasp and 1/2 rhubarb for this recipe! I may need to use a bit more maple syrup since rhubarb is much more sour than raspberries, but I do like some of the sour.  ;)
